  "detailed_description": "Cozy Island Idle is a chill fishing idle game where you catch all sort of fantasy fishes to showcase them in an Aquarium to sell them to turn a profit and customize your aquarium and island.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2628400/extras/1b37038a39601273730a024af0f42f4c.avif?t=1739655258\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>☕A Casual and Relaxing Fishing Idle Game with hours of entertainment;<br></li><li>🏝️ Beautiful Graphics and Relaxing Ambience;<br></li><li>🐠 Customize your Aquarium and Island;<br></li><li>🎧  Relaxing Lo-fi musics;<br></li><li>👜 Buy upgrades to get new themed fishes;<br></li><li>🎀 Many secrets for you to discover;<br></li><li>🎒 Fully interactive Inventory System;<br></li><li>🍅 A pomodoro timer while playing;<br></li><li>⚙️ A Satisfying progression system</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2628400/extras/9c7b28dc0999c7a94b0c5af44c2967e4.avif?t=1739655258\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2628400/extras/5b39b06567b778a92181d7c1387d1c28.poster.avif?t=1739655258\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2628400/extras/5b39b06567b778a92181d7c1387d1c28.webm?t=1739655258\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2628400/extras/5b39b06567b778a92181d7c1387d1c28.mp4?t=1739655258\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2628400/extras/db78c830cfd21ba19b2560ab054b27c6.avif?t=1739655258\" wi